snippet.title: Skate Fish - Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description: Get ready to impress fish with some sick skateboarding tricks. Check out the latest trailer to see gameplay and more from Skate Fish, an upcoming skateboard-meets-fishing game where the only way to catch fish is to impress them. Skate Fish launches on iOS and Android on March 28, 2024.
